content.raw:
Thanks for the contribution!

I see that you've included some URDF and ROS related files, such as `package.xml`. Unfortunately, this repository only hosts SDF files. Also, the repository expects a specific directory structure which is not followed on this PR.

Please refer to [this](http://gazebosim.org/tutorials?tut=model_contrib&cat=) tutorial for additional info.
